<div class="requesting clear_fix">
  <div class="loading_layer">
    <p class="weixin_ico"></p>
    <p class="weixin_text">通讯中，请稍候...</p>
  </div>
  <div class="attached_box">
    <div class="border_1px layer_head">
      <div class="title">帐号绑定</div>
    </div>
    <div class="attached_content">
      <div class="wx_txt clear_fix">
        <p>已有账号请绑定，否则将为您创建一个新帐号</p>
      </div>
      <form id="binding_form" method="post">
        <div class="suffix_tip hide">
          <div class="tip_angle"></div>
          <span class="left">sina.com</span>
          <span class="left">qq.com</span>
          <span class="left">163.com</span>
          <span class="left">yahoo.com</span>
          <span class="left">126.com</span>
          <span class="left">sohu.com</span>
          <div class="clear"></div>
        </div>
        <p class="email read_in">
          <span class="left">帐号</span>
          <input class="left" type="email" name="username" placeholder="邮箱或者手机号码">
          <span class="clear_txt hide"><em class="sprites"></em></span>
        </p><div class="clear"></div>
        <p></p>
        <p class="psd read_in">
          <span class="left">密码</span>
          <input class="left" type="password" name="password" placeholder="您的密码">
          <span class="clear_txt hide"><em class="sprites"></em></span>
        </p><div class="clear"></div>
        <p></p>
        <div class="binding_btn btn" id="binding_submit">
          <span>绑定帐号</span>
          <style type="text/css">
              /*body{
                -webkit-transform: translate(0,0,0);
                -webkit-backface-visibility:hidden;
              }*/
              .loading16{
                  top:-31px;
                  width: 100px;
                  height: 100px;
                  position: relative;
                  left: 50%;
                  margin:0;
                  margin-left: -50px;
                  border-radius: 100px;
                  -webkit-border-radius: 100px;
                  -webkit-animation-duration:1.5s;
                  -webkit-animation-iteration-count:infinite;
                  -webkit-animation-timing-function:linear;
                  -webkit-animation-name: rotateThis16;
                  -moz-border-radius: 100px;
                  -moz-animation-duration:1.5s;
                  -moz-animation-iteration-count:infinite;
                  -moz-animation-timing-function:linear;
                  -moz-animation-name: rotateThis16;
              }
              @-webkit-keyframes rotateThis16{
                  from {-webkit-transform: scale(0.18) rotate(0deg);}
                  to {-webkit-transform: scale(0.18) rotate(360deg);}
              }
              @-moz-keyframes rotateThis16{
                  from {-moz-transform: scale(0.18) rotate(0deg);}
                  to {-moz-transform: scale(0.18) rotate(360deg);}
              }
              .loading16 > div{
                  width: 18px;
                  height: 18px;
                  background-color: #fff;
                  -webkit-border-radius: 30px;
                  -moz-border-radius: 30px;
                  -o-border-radius: 30px;
                  border-radius: 30px;
                  position: absolute;
                  left: 41px;
                  top: 41px;
              }

              .bar1{
                  opacity: 0.3;
                  -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg) translate(0, -42px);
                  -moz-transform: rotate(0deg) translate(0, -42px);
              }
              .bar2{
                  opacity: 0.4;
                  -webkit-transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -42px);
                  -moz-transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -42px);
              }
              .bar3{
                  opacity: 0.5;
                  -webkit-transform: rotate(90deg) translate(0, -42px);
                  -moz-transform: rotate(90deg) translate(0, -42px);
              }
              .bar4{
                  opacity: 0.6;
                  -webkit-transform: rotate(135deg) translate(0, -42px);
                  -moz-transform: rotate(135deg) translate(0, -42px);
              }
              .bar5{
                  opacity: 0.7;
                  -webkit-transform: rotate(180deg) translate(0, -42px);
                  -moz-transform: rotate(180deg) translate(0, -42px);
              }
              .bar6{
                  opacity: 0.8;
                  -webkit-transform: rotate(225deg) translate(0, -42px);
                  -moz-transform: rotate(225deg) translate(0, -42px);
              }
              .bar7{
                  opacity: 0.9;
                  -webkit-transform: rotate(270deg) translate(0, -42px);
                  -moz-transform: rotate(270deg) translate(0, -42px);
              }
              .bar8{
                  opacity: 1;
                  -webkit-transform: rotate(315deg) translate(0, -42px);
                  -moz-transform: rotate(315deg) translate(0, -42px);
              }
          </style>
          <div class="order_load">
            <div class="loading16">
              <div class="bar1"></div>
              <div class="bar2"></div>
              <div class="bar3"></div>
              <div class="bar4"></div>
              <div class="bar5"></div>
              <div class="bar6"></div>
              <div class="bar7"></div>
              <div class="bar8"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
        <input type="submit" value="" class="register_submit">
        <div class="create_btn btn">创建帐号<div class="down_shadow"></div></div>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<script type="text/javascript">
    loading.initialize();
</script>
